{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be innovative and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Red Canvas Designs</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e52b50; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f8c8dc; /* Lighter shade of red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4.5em;\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section-content {\n            max-width: 700px;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 280px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 50px 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        .animate-fade-in {\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(20px);\n            animation: fadeIn 1s forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .hero h1, .hero p {\n            animation: slideInFromTop 1.5s ease-out forwards;\n            opacity: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            animation-delay: 0.5s;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            animation-delay: 1s;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            animation-delay: 1.5s;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideInFromTop {\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .section {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .section-content {\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Red Canvas Designs</h1>\n        <p>Bringing your vision to vibrant life with innovative design solutions.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Let's Create Together</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"section-content animate-fade-in\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <p>We offer a comprehensive range of design services tailored to elevate your brand and captivate your audience. From striking web design to compelling branding, we are your partners in creativity.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card animate-fade-in\">\n            <h3>Web Design</h3>\n            <p>Crafting responsive, user-friendly, and visually stunning websites that leave a lasting impression.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card animate-fade-in\">\n            <h3>Branding & Identity</h3>\n            <p>Developing unique brand identities that resonate with your target market and drive recognition.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card animate-fade-in\">\n            <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n            <p>Creating intuitive and engaging user experiences that delight your customers.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"section-content animate-fade-in\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At Red Canvas Designs, we believe in the power of bold ideas and meticulous execution. Our passion for design drives us to push boundaries and deliver exceptional results for every client. We are a team of dedicated creatives committed to your success.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-form\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Red Canvas Designs. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.classList.add('animate-fade-in');\n                        observer.unobserve(entry.target);\n                    }\n                });\n            }, { threshold: 0.1 });\n\n            document.querySelectorAll('.animate-fade-in').forEach(element => {\n                observer.observe(element);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}